long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
QuickTag is an extension which can quick-open your bookmarks or browsing history.

* Bookmarks or browsing history can be quickly found.
* Conveniently reopen them.
* Search the specified keyword.
